## Priority 4 — Data Persistence (in-memory via stores)

### Pet Detail (`lib/screens/pet_detail/pet_detail_screen.dart`)

| Status | Item | Details |
|--------|------|---------|
| WORKS | "Add Note" | Adds to local `_notes` list; shows snackbar |
| NOT PERSISTED | Notes lost on navigation | `_notes` is local state in the widget |
| MOCK | Measurement history | From `MockData.princessMeasurements` |
| MOCK | Clinical notes | From `MockData.princessNotes` / `maxNotes` |
| MISSING | Edit pet info | Screen is read-only |

**Fix:** Replace local `_notes` with `noteStore.getNotes(pet.name)` and `noteStore.addNote(...)`. Replace measurement history with `measurementStore.getMeasurements(pet.name)`.

